<h1>Welcome to Movie Tracker</h1>

<h3>About:</h3>
<p>Have you ever sat down on your comfy couch after a long day, ready to watch a movie and relax but you can't quite numb out just yet since you just don't know what to watch? Movie Tracker can help with that! After you create an account, you'll be able to generate 20 random movies to choose from with the simple click of a button. Movie Tracker allows you to browse through these movies and read about some details such as the description, who stars in it, and the runtime, among other things. If you love the movie, or just want to save it for later, you can add the movie to your favorites to make sure you don't forget about it. Movie Tracker also allows you to keep track of your favorite snacks so you're well prepared for that well-deserved movie-watching session. Just create an account and let Movie Tracker do the rest!</p>
